description: Redevelopment of the site to comprise of the erection of a 3 to 6 storey residential development of 116 dwellings (31 x 1 bed, 54 x 2 bed, 21 x 3 bed, 7 x 4 bed and 3 x 5 bed), and Artists Studios (1000 sq.m.); semi-basement parking for 53 cars and 6 off-street, including motorcycle and bicycle parking and new vehicular access to Dunedin Road.
